Description: The digitized historical manuscripts held in the special collections of the Norwegian university of science and technology (NTNU).The data is a catalogue of manuscripts held by NTNU and these are catalogued directly as RDF.The data is the usage catalogue for the Gunnerus Library Special Collections- and drives their web presences. The data is under constant development and the dataset is growing- and must be seen as unstable. Links to fulltext will be added as these are digitized
